<div style="font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: auto;">
  <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
  <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
  <p>We received a request to reset your password. Click the button below to
    choose a new one. This link expires in 1 hour.</p>
  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a
      href="{{resetLink}}"
      style="background-color: #007bff; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;"
    >
      Reset Password
    </a>
  </div>
  <p>If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
  <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee;" />
  <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #777;">Sent from {{appName}} Support</p>
</div>